Olladra Smiles was a tavern and performance
hall in [[Metrol]] beloved by the students of the [[Wynarn Institute of Art]], who often called it just “the Smile.” While far smaller than similar establishments on
[[Southshore]], many famous entertainers played
their first shows on their stage.